ct|argdefs=q:string!@query(搜索关键词，必填);category:string@query;district:string@query|outputs=id,name,category,district,latitude,longitude|hints=地标模糊搜索。\\nget_landmark_by_id|GET /api/landmarks/{id}|intent=search|required=id|params=id|argdefs=id:string!@path(地标 ID，如 SS_001...)|outputs=id,name,category,district,latitude,longitude|hints=按地标 ID 查询详情。\\nget_landmark_stats|GET /api/landmarks/stats|intent=search|required=-|params=-|argdefs=-|outputs=total,by_category,by_district|hints=地标统计，不用于具体找房。\\nget_house_by_id|GET /api/houses/{house_id}|intent=house_detail|required=house_id|params=house_id|argdefs=house_id:string!@path(房源 ID，如 HF_200...)|outputs=house_id,listing_platform,rent,layout,area,district,community,subway_distance,commute_to_xierqi_min,status,tags,decoration,elevator,orientation,available_date|hints=单套房源详情。\\nget_house_listings|GET /api/houses/listings/{house_id}|intent=listings|required=house_id|params=house_id|argdefs=house_id:string!@path(房源 ID，如 HF_200...)|outputs=total,page_size,items[].listing_platform,items[].rent,items[].status,items[].url|hints=同一房源在多平台挂牌价格/状态查询。\\nget_houses_by_community|GET /api/houses/by_community|intent=search|required=community|params=community,listing_platform,page,page_size|argdefs=community:string!@query(小区名，与数据一致，如 建清...);listing_platform:string@query=链家/安居客/58同城;page:integer@query;page_size:integer@query|outputs=total,page_size,items[].house_id,items[].listing_platform,items[].rent,items[].layout,items[].district,items[].community,items[].subway_distance,items[].status|hints=给定小区名时优先。\\nget_houses_by_platform|GET /api/houses/by_platform|intent=search|required=-|params=listing_platform,district,area,min_price,max_price,bedrooms,rental_type,decoration,orientation,elevator,min_area,max_area,property_type,subway_line,max_subway_dist,subway_station,utilities_type,available_from_before,commute_to_xierqi_max,sort_by,sort_order,page,page_size|argdefs=listing_platform:string@query=链家/安居客/58同城;district:string@query;area:string@query;min_p